dcterms:description: Food101N consists of 365k images crawled from various sources using the Food-101 taxonomy, with an annotation accuracy of about 80%. It is used as a noisy dataset in the experiments.

dcterms:description: Clothing1M contains 1 million images of clothes with 14 categories, where most labels are generated from surrounding text on the web, leading to a low annotation accuracy of 61.54%. It serves as a noisy dataset in the experiments.
dcterms:title: Clothing1M
